## AppDataStream type

Third (or first) party providers of analytics, metrics, and monitoring that are hooked up to receive transactional information about the app.

<b>Signature:</b>

```typescript
export declare type AppDataStream = BespokenDataStream | ChatbaseDataStream | GoogleAnalyticsStream | VoiceLabsDataStream | LuisDataStream | DialogflowDataStream | DashbotDataStream;
```
